# Import Workflow

The import process follows a specific workflow implemented across several classes:

## Import Process Flow

1. File Handling:
   - File upload via AJAX: [class-md-import-force-ajax-handler.php](mdc:includes/class-md-import-force-ajax-handler.php)
   - File processing: [class-md-import-force-file-processor.php](mdc:includes/class-md-import-force-file-processor.php)

2. Content Import:
   - Import coordination: [class-md-import-force-import-manager.php](mdc:includes/class-md-import-force-import-manager.php)
   - Progress tracking: [class-md-import-force-progress-tracker.php](mdc:includes/class-md-import-force-progress-tracker.php)

3. Specific Content Importers:
   - Posts: [class-md-import-force-post-importer.php](mdc:includes/class-md-import-force-post-importer.php)
   - Taxonomies: [class-md-import-force-taxonomy-importer.php](mdc:includes/class-md-import-force-taxonomy-importer.php)
   - Media: [class-md-import-force-media-handler.php](mdc:includes/class-md-import-force-media-handler.php)
   - Comments: [class-md-import-force-comment-importer.php](mdc:includes/class-md-import-force-comment-importer.php)

4. URL Management:
   - URL Handling: [class-md-import-force-url-handler.php](mdc:includes/class-md-import-force-url-handler.php)
   
5. Logging and Error Handling:
   - Error tracking: [class-md-import-force-error-handler.php](mdc:includes/class-md-import-force-error-handler.php)
   - Log management: [class-md-import-force-logger.php](mdc:includes/class-md-import-force-logger.php)

## Frontend Implementation

The client-side import process is managed by [import.js](mdc:assets/js/admin/import.js), which handles:
- AJAX requests during import
- Progress updates
- Error reporting
